{
  "texts": [
    "The values in the table correspond to the mean and standard deviation of those mean F 1 scores per template.",
    "The generative approach performs better than the extractive one on the Medication templates (0.48 vs. 0.34 and 0.62 vs. 0.53 F 1 score for type 2 diabetes and glaucoma, respec- tively).",
    "On the Population and Outcome template, the results are mixed with one approach performing better for one disease dataset but not for the other.",
    "On all six remaining templates, the extractive approach performs better, although with different margins.Mean F 1 scores per slot are shown in Table 7 in the Appendix 2, again with mean and standard deviation (of the mean F 1 scores) calculated for the 10 models trained using the best hyperparameters of their respective category.",
